{"type":"message","id":"de3e0af9","parentId":"c68fa0d6","timestamp":"2026-04-14T16:19:06.134Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e Agent Status to Lead] You are Orbis. Check sessions_list and compile a brief status of all ACTIVE master-orchestrator sessions (excluding this cron session).\n\nFor each active session, report:\n- Session key (shortened)\n- Status (running/done)\n- What it's doing (from context)\n- How long it's been running\n\nSend the report to Lead directly via sessions_send to sessionKey: agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134\n\nFormat:\n🌐 Orbis — Agent Status | {HH:MM} UTC {DD MMM}\n\nActive sessions: N\n• [session name]: [status] — [task/description] — [duration]\n\nIf only this cron session is active (no other sessions), send HEARTBEAT_OK only.\nIf there are no sessions at all, stay SILENT.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 14th, 2026 - 4:18 PM (UTC) / 2026-04-14 16:18 UTC"}],"timestamp":1776183545934}}
